		<a href="MSG_MailBox.asp?mode=new&amp;sendto=Bakanar">
		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/privatemsg.gif" border="0" alt="Click Here to Message Bakanar" width="22" height="11"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
		
		<a href="MB_editmsg.asp?FID=60&FN=Bard&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=2022044&TN=soloing&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=2022105&PL=4">
		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/edit.gif" border="0" alt="Edit/Delete Message" width="18" height="13"></a>
		
		</font>
		<hr size="1">Gear matters very little.  You can solo from 1 to 65 as a Bard, relatively quickly and with little danger and the exact methods you use to do so will depend on your personal style of play.  Some people fear/snare mobs and pound on them as they run away, some chant kite them, some people swarm kite, most do some combination of the above with some grouping mixed in as well.  From about 27 or so up, gear isn't terribly important, yes, nice gear is good, increased mana pool, more hp, etc, all are nice but not essential to playing a bard, as long as you have a good drum and at least the basic versions of your other instruments you're all set.</P><P>Personally I do a lot of charming and when I do chant kite I like to mix in DD songs so I went for a larger mana pool and Flowing thought items for my bard.</P><P>How to solo?  At 12 I was just tanking mobs in Paludal, at 13 I started pulling red and yellow con mushrooms, they run slower than you do so it's easy to Bellow kite them if they start beating you up too bad in melee... just turn on Boastful Bellow and run around, they'll chase you and lose hp, the end.  I stayed in Paludal till 25.</P><P>At 25 you get your first damage shield, I used this, personal haste/combat buffs and snare to kill needlites from 25 to 32 then I went to the Overthere, soloed sarnaks and such, charming and bellow kiting till 36 or so then I went to the Dreadlands and did the same but with giants and such near the glacier... avoided the spiders since they snared, nuked and rooted ya.</P><P>Alternated between EW, BW and DL all the way to 52 when I went to PoN and   stayed there pretty much till now... I'll ding 59 next time I play.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
	</td>
