		<hr size="1">Chant Kiting is basically DoTing the mob to death with 1-4 DoTs while you run then around in a circle.</P><P>In any case, addressing the original post, I went through my levels much the same way as was already stated. However, I really suggest grouping quite a bit as well. Soloing uses a set of songs that are completely different from the ones you will use in a group setting. It is important to get a good understanding on how to use all your songs.</P><P>Anyway, just my word of warning, even though I have spent most of my xping time soloing as well.</P><P><BR>Wizard of the 55th Circle of Knowledge.<BR>Bard of the 51st silly song.<BR>Beasty of the 23rd soloing level.<BR>Shadow Knight of the 3rd level of Evil.<BR>12th level maker of viscous mana (Enchanter)</P><P>"There is always one more imbecile than you had planned for."<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
